changefont and resize might only work on xfcce4. 
Therefore if not on xfce4 should use playMovie.sh, otherwise playMovie0.sh and should setup output0/ with the resolution specified
generally, 
1. put image into data/ , and run . makeMovie.sh 60 15
2. add . $root/playmovie.sh in ~/.bashrc

for hgih resolution
1. make sure changefont and resize work
2. find appropriate resolution with testsize.sh
3. run makeMovie.sh with proper arguments
4. add . $root/playmovie0.sh in ~/.bashrc
